item.description:
Comet and Holly wanted to see some of their friends and show everyone around Riverside Park! I think it will be great to get the dogs out and explore a new place with all sorts of new smells!! And the best part is that they can run off some excess energy!!!! Hope to see some of you there!!!!

Jamie, Comet and Holly!
item.how_to_find_us: We will meet at the end of Sundeen Pky in the parking lot for the park
